Class JpaTransactionWrapper

java.lang.Object
org.keycloak.models.map.storage.jpa.JpaTransactionWrapper
All Implemented Interfaces:
KeycloakTransaction
public class JpaTransactionWrapper extends Object implements KeycloakTransaction
Wraps an EntityTransaction as a KeycloakTransaction so it can be enlisted in KeycloakTransactionManager.
